    "body" : "<p>Use the <code>continue</code> keyword. Read <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/java/nutsandbolts/branch.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a>.</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>The continue statement skips the current iteration of a for, while , or do-while loop.</p>\n</blockquote>\n"
