    "body" : "<p>use <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/java/nutsandbolts/branch.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">continue</a> keyword .</p>\n\n<p><strong>EX:</strong></p>\n\n<pre><code>for(int i = 0; i &lt; 10; i++){\n  if(i == 5){\n    continue;\n   }\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
